(10, 105, 'Senior . NET Developer', 'anujkulkarni86@gmail.com', '0738206162', '[\".Net\",\"C#\"]', '[\"backend developer\",\"Javascript Developer\"]', '0', 0, 'SE', 'Stockholm', 'Software Developer Lead with 7+ years of experience in the\nInformation Technology working in various roles in distributed industry\nsectors and verticals. Have experience on Microsoft Technologies like\nSharePoint and .NET in global projects as consultant .\nWeb Developer with the knowledge and expertise in several back end\nlanguages as well as client side technologies such as JavaScript, HTML5,\nAngularJS and CSS3, I have worked on many projects using a various\nnumber of techniques and skills as .NET framework (versions: 2.0, 3.5, 4.0,\nand 4.5), SQL server, JavaScript, jQuery, AJAX, Linq, Entity framework,\nXML. A team player with a positive mindset, curious and proactive in his\nrole who enjoys trying new areas and challenges. Excellent communication\nskills, problem solving and inter-personal skills, leadership qualities,\nstrong communication.', 1, '2021-01-26 07:44:30', '2021-01-26 07:44:30'),
