(25, 140, 'Backend developer', 'sadat.sweden@gmail.com', '+46736816016', '[\".Net\",\"Agile\",\"Backend development\",\"Bootstrap\",\"C#\",\"development\",\"frontend\",\"Fullstack Javascript\",\"Git\",\"html\",\"Java\",\"Java backend\",\"Javascript\"]', '[\"API Developer\",\"backend developer\",\"developer\",\"frontend developer\",\"fullstack developer\",\"Javascript Developer\",\"Software Engineer\"]', '0', 0, 'SE', 'Stockholm', 'Stable study background and competence in programming and problem solving especially in Java, C# .Net, SQL,ASP.NET, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, jQuery, Angular, SharePoint, and different code libraries. Looking forward to a new career start and interested in software/web development. As a person, I am flexible, calm, loyal, positive, able to adapt to changes. I am a perfect team player with leadership skills and I enjoy challenges and learning new things.', 1, '2021-02-01 03:36:10', '2021-02-01 03:36:10'),
