(32, 147, 'Steve Watson', 'designerofthings@gmail.com', '0700190723', '[\"Agile\",\"Bootstrap\",\"css\",\"development\",\"frontend\",\"Fullstack Javascript\",\"GraphQL\",\"Javascript\",\"Node.js\",\"Product design\",\"React\",\"React.js\",\"REST API\",\"Ruby on Rails\",\"SASS\",\"Scrum\",\"Testing\",\"UX\\/UI Designer\"]', '[\"developer\",\"frontend developer\",\"fullstack developer\",\"Javascript Developer\"]', '0', 0, 'SE', 'Stockholm', 'Hi,  I am at the start of my developing career, looking for a junior position.  I have full stack skills but enjoy frontend the most.   As you can see from my Github profile, I have created numerous ReactJS applications and React Native mobile applications, so I have a good base of knowledge in Javascript and the React library.  I also really enjoy HTML and CSS, both using a framework and vanilla CSS. <br />\n<br />\nI currently work with React to create a platform for a circular economy startup. I also have a great interest and education in design and speak English and Swedish. <br />\nAs a person, I am calm, focused and easy to work with. I enjoy cooking, drinking fine wine and running (not at the same time!). <br />\nI look forward to hearing from you.<br />\nBest regards,<br />\nSteve Watson', 0, '2021-02-04 10:17:33', '2021-02-04 10:17:33'),
(33, 151, 'Javier Escano', 'javier.es.val@gmail.com', '+34 680 980 804', '[\"Assembler\",\"C++\",\"OpenGL\",\"Unity\",\"Unreal Engine\"]', '[\"developer\",\"Unity\"]', '0', 0, 'ES', 'Madrid', 'Studied Videogame Programming at ESAT Valencia.<br /><br />\nWorked for 3 years at Grupo Franco as a game develpoer using C++ with their own game engine<br /><br />\nExperience using Unity and UE4 in both blueprints and code.<br /><br />\nMade my own game engine from scratch using OpenGL.<br /><br />\nKnowledge of mobile monetization, best practices and what to avoid.<br /><br />\nFluent in English and Spanish.', 0, '2021-02-07 09:53:46', '2021-02-07 14:51:41'),
(34, 152, 'Bartosz Kruba', 'bartosz.kruba@gmail.com', '0729028894', '[\"Angular.js\",\"Fullstack Javascript\",\"Java\",\"Node.js\",\"PHP\",\"React.js\",\"Vue.js\",\"Spring\"]', '[\"backend developer\",\"frontend developer\",\"fullstack developer\",\"Javascript Developer\",\"PHP Developer\",\"Java Developer\"]', '0', 0, 'SE', 'Arlv', 'I am a programmer with a wide range of skills who is not afraid to learn new things. I am a competent backend and frontend developer with some extra skills in the machine learning domain. My three strongest languages are Java, Javascript and PHP but I also have some experience in Python, Kotlin, Typescript and C#.\n\nMy LinkedIn Profile: https://www.linkedin.com/in/bartosz-kruba-044ba6171/', 0, '2021-02-07 13:38:50', '2021-02-07 13:38:50'),
