(41, 95, 'Platform Software Engineer', 'Global technology provider in the travel industry', NULL, '[\"Couchbase\",\"Docker\",\"Java\",\"Jenkins\",\"Kubernetes\",\"Node.js\",\"Python\",\"React.js\",\"SQL\"]', '0', 0, 'SE', 'Gteborg', 'Are you a fan of clean code, architecture and the latest technologies for scalable web applications?<br />\n<br />\nWe are looking for a Developer/Software Engineer with previous experience in scalable web applications and platforms for a global technology provider in the travel industry. If you are skilled and interested in improving existing systems, you might be the person we are looking for. We can promise you a nice mix of architecture, software development and making sure our client is working with the latest solutions and technologies.<br />\n<br />\nWhat you will do<br />\n<br />\nYou will be part of our client\'s Platform Team and in collaboration with colleagues you will work to improve systems, tools and processes in order to simplify for the development teams implementation and deployment of new functionality.<br />\n<br />\nYour support will be provided through automation using building systems, pipelines and refactoring of existing code. If you also have an interest in new scalable technologies, e.g. Docker, Kubernetes, Kafka and NoSQL databases you will really enjoy working with us.<br />\n<br />\nRequirements<br />\n<br />\nTechnical skills<br />\n<br />\nAcademic education in the IT field or equivalent education Previous experience of scalable web applications Excellent communication skills in English, oral presentations and in writing. Our client operates in a mixed Linux environment in our data centers and AWS so knowledge, or interest, in these environments is simply said, very good!<br />\n<br />\nPersonal traits It is important to play as a team and we love that you see solutions where others see problems. In your job you will be providing support to colleagues, so it is important that you can switch between different work tasks and you don\'t mind being interrupted. You have a positive mindset and are motivated by challenging projects; new and existing. Rest assured, we have a lot going on around here! Of course you, like us, are passionate about what you do and keep up to date on best practices in your areas of expertise.<br />\n<br />\nDue to the pandemic, and the difficulties of relocating, we wish that you are located in Sweden, and have a valid work permit, when applying for this position.<br />\n<br />\nBenefits You will become part of a tight-knit team of about 80 people, all of which with different skills and personalities and we believe that it is precisely this that makes our client such a great team. The ambition however is shared  we strive for the same goals, are passionate about what we do and work hard at a high pace.<br />\n<br />\nOffice in the City  Our client is located in central Gothenburg, a stone\'s throw from public transport and lunch restaurants.<br />\n<br />\nConferences  Our client believe in personal development and continuous education. As an employee, you receive a generous budget each year to spend at conferences, online courses or other means to learn new things. In addition to this, our client continuously organize internal trainings and workshops so that we can learn from each other.<br />\n<br />\nHealthcare allowance  Each employee receives a maximum allowable amount each year according to the Swedish Tax Agency to spend on health-promoting activities such as a gym card, massage etc.<br />\n<br />\nPension and health insurance  Through partners we offer a comprehensive pension and health insurance so that you can get help quickly in case of an accident.<br />\n<br />\nHackaton and Dev week  We believe in fostering creativity and testing new things. Therefore, our client have recurring Hackaton and Dev weeks where the teams decide what they want to work on.<br />\n<br />\nIn addition to this our client even serves you breakfast every morning.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-01-20 10:14:55', '2021-01-20 11:29:54'),
(42, 100, 'Backend developer', 'Additude', NULL, '[\".Net\",\"Backend development\",\"C#\",\"Java\",\"Node.js\"]', '0', 0, 'SE', 'Malm', 'Additude is a company in the forefront of technology, offering consultancy services within innovation, software and headhunting.\n\nWe are now looking for a driven and motivated consultant who wants to work with exciting companies and grow together with other driven colleagues. All while working with the latest technology. Together we find assignments that are just right for you and your career goals. We aim to offer a rewarding employment with generous perks and terms. <br /><br />\n<br /><br />\nWith over 300 customers within IT & Tech, we can always make sure you get an assignment that is fulfilling and interesting to you. If not, we find a better match. We want to help you develop yourself, your skills and your resume.<br /><br />\n<br /><br />\nWhat we are looking for:<br /><br />\n<br /><br />\nA minimum of 4 years relevant experience.<br /><br />\nExperience mainly from backend development with .Net, C#, Java, GO, Node.js.<br /><br />\n<br /><br />\nIf you have experience with cloud technologies that is a plus.<br /><br />\n<br /><br />\nFurthermore you have experience with and prefer an agile working process.<br /><br />\n<br /><br />\nYou have a degree in computer science or equivalent.<br /><br />\n<br /><br />\nYou speak and write both Swedish and English on a professional level.<br /><br />\n<br /><br />\nAt Additude we want to exceed our customers, partners and colleagues expectations. We want them to be delighted. We are ambitious, committed and happy<br /><br />\n<br /><br />\nShowing consideration and respect is a natural value for us. We work together and are keen to help each other succeed. We treat others as we ourselves would like to be treated. We encourage, give praise and are proud of our colleagues and the contributions of others. Job satisfaction is something we all feel and something for which we all take responsibility.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-01-21 17:15:57', '2021-02-04 09:56:11'),
(43, 107, 'Senior . NET Developer', 'Valtech', NULL, '[\".Net\",\"C#\"]', '0', 0, 'SE', 'Stockholm', 'We have a strong culture of sharing our skills and in this role you will be an important part of it. We believe that you yourself are strengthened in your role by teaching and inspiring others.\r\n\r\nWe have customers in several different industries with many fun and varied digital projects that you will come in contact with. For example, you will be able to work with various .NET projects such as large international e-commerce websites with advanced integrations or perhaps campaign websites for well-known companies. In the projects, it is you who takes the lead and shows the way.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-01-25 13:03:03', '2021-01-25 13:03:03'),
(44, 103, 'C/C++/C#/Unity Developer', 'Gaming Company', NULL, '[\"C#\",\"C++\",\"Unity\",\"C\",\"Gamedevelopment\"]', '0', 0, 'SE', 'Stockholm', 'C# / C++ / C with 5+ years of experience. <br />\nIf you have Unity or experience in game programming its a huge advantage for this position. <br />\n<br />\nYou will join one of our direct clients - a game production company with several well known titles.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-01-26 13:42:51', '2021-01-26 19:45:10'),
(45, 103, 'Sr Android Developer Consultant', 'Just Tech - Consultant Company', NULL, '[\"Android\",\"fintech\"]', '0', 0, 'SE', 'Stockholm', 'We are looking for a senior android developer, 5+ yrs of java/android, to join us at Just Tech as a consultant in our company. Our customer is a mayor fintech company in Stockholm growing their android team. We can offer a good team and environment, market level salaries, bonus and a lot of flexible work-life balance. You will work 37.5 hours per week.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-01-26 19:44:25', '2021-01-26 19:44:25'),
(46, 139, 'Frontend Developer', 'Kumpan', NULL, '[\"Angular.js\",\"css\",\"html\",\"Javascript\",\"React\",\"React.js\",\"typescript\"]', '0', 0, 'SE', 'Stockholm', 'Bli vr kumpan!\nDu kan vlja och vraka mellan jobben. nd tror vi att det r hos oss du vill arbeta. Det vill vi ju sjlva! Varenda dag anstrnger vi oss fr att gra Kumpan till en arbetsplats att trivas p.\n\nDetta r vad vi kommit fram till hittills:\n\nArbete r inte allt hr i livet\nDrfr har vi 7 timmars arbetsdag. Under de timmarna kan tempot vara hgt, men vi bryter av med konferenser, seminarier och en liten AW ibland. Dessutom maxar vi friskvrdsbidraget och har en riktigt bra sjukvrdsfrskring.\n\nDet ska lna sig att arbeta\nBra folk ska ha bra ln. Och bra pensionsavsttning. Sedan tycker vi att det r roligare att jobba nr man delar p frukterna av arbetet. Hr r alla med och delar p vinsten!\n\nVi r alla mnniskor\nKumpaner tar hand om varandra. Vi hjlps t nr det r motigt och glds tillsammans nr det gr bra. Tack och lov har vi gott om medvind!\n\nKumpaner r konsulter med gemenskap\nSpeciellt i tider utan Covid-restriktioner. P fredagar samlas vi p kontoret och arbetar tillsammans. D kan vi sl vra kloka huvuden ihop, lsa vra kunders problem med gemensamma krafter och kka lunch med varandra. Ibland tar vi en l eller tv framt eftermiddagen. Eller en kaffe. Huvudsaken r att vi fr umgs.\n\nDu har ungefr fem rs erfarenhet av utveckling\nSkerligen r du en nyfiken person, en sdan som lskar att skaffa sig nya kunskaper. Sdana fr du nmligen hr. Vi jobbar med mnga tech-stacks och en del av dem r frmodligen nya fr dig. Vi r sjlva framfrallt vassa p open source, och tror att det r dr du trivs bst ocks.\n\nDu gillar att dela med dig av din kunskap\nKumpaner lr av varandra, och vid dagens slut ska var och en av oss kunna lite mer n vi kunde nr vi steg upp p morgonen. Det r krvande ibland, men ocks vldigt, vldigt roligt.\n\nDet du behver kunna redan nr du kommer hit r:\nDu behver framfrallt lska JavaScript. Vi ser grna att du har ungefr 5 rs arbetslivserfarenhet i bagaget. Sen ser vi grna att du tidigare suttit med ramverk som React, Angular eller Vue.\nBygga applikationer frn grunden. Din kod r prydlig och gr att teranvnda, frsts. Du r ju ett proffs!\nDu trivs med att sitta hos kund och arbeta, men eftersom att vi trivs ihop som arbetskumpaner ser du fram emot fredagssamlingen p kontoret.\nHar du dessutom kunskaper som kan hjlpa oss i utvecklingen av vr egen CI/CD-plattform r det ett stort plus.\n\nLite mer om oss\nVi r en webb- och konsultbyr som funnits sedan 2004. Vi utvecklar webb och appar i open source-milj, och r jkligt vassa p grafik och teknik. Dessutom har vi kunder av vitt skilda slag med olika tech stacks och individuella utmaningar. Kontoret ligger uppe p Mosebacke, precis bredvid Sdra teatern. Har du frgor r du alltid vlkommen att kontakta oss p hr@kumpan.se.\n\nGlada hlsningar, Dina framtida kumpaner.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-01-29 12:01:48', '2021-01-29 12:01:48'),
